# p4c build artifacts. The only committed p4info *for quackmpp.p4* is the test
# fixture at P4R-Type/src/test/resources/quackmpp_exchange.p4info.json —
# anything p4c writes next to the .p4 source is scratch. A second committed copy
# in examples/ was read by nothing and drifted silently.
# (Other p4infos are committed for other P4 programs and are unaffected:
# legacy_actionprofile, read by QuackMppTypegenSuite; and the config* fixtures
# behind the examples/ Scala packages and vm/files/Makefile. README.md:109 runs
# typegen against config1.p4info.json.)
*.p4i
P4R-Type/examples/src/main/p4/quackmpp.json
P4R-Type/examples/src/main/p4/quackmpp.p4info.json
P4R-Type/examples/src/main/p4/quackmpp.vm-era.p4info.json
